visual.name: Enlighten Aquarium
visual.description: Data should be simple and engaging. Data should tell a story at a glance. Data should be FUN! Enlighten aquarium tells a story through making your data simple, fun and engaging. It can be used in various situations like a dashboard screen in a room where everyone can see it and notice changes day to day and empathise with the data to rally efforts.

dataRoles.name: Category
dataRoles.description: The categorical field to repesent as fish

dataRoles.name: Legend
dataRoles.description: The categorical field to show as different types of fish

dataRoles.name: Series
dataRoles.description: The numeric amount representing the size of each fish

dataRoles.name: FishSpeed
dataRoles.description: The numeric amount representing the speed of each fish

dataRoles.name: YAxis
dataRoles.description: The numeric amount used to position the fish on the vertical axis

dataRoles.name: Tooltips
dataRoles.description: Add additional data fields that people can see in the tooltip when they hover on part of this visualization.

style.description: Select the style of the title

key.description: Key required to unlock. Contact publisher.

theme.description: The background and style of the fish

maxsize.description: Specify a typical largest value in your dataset to set the size scale of all the fish. This allows you to keep the size consistent even if your data changes.

maxspeed.description: Specify a typical largest value in your dataset to set the speed scale of all the fish. This allows you to keep the speed consistent even if your data changes.
